'''Play! Pokémon Prize Pack Series One''' is a series of promotional cards released through [[Play! Pokémon|Pokémon Organized Play]] events or affiliated products. This set features 170 specifically selected cards from the {{TCG|Sword & Shield}} expansion through {{TCG|Evolving Skies}} in addition to {{TCG|SWSH Black Star Promos}} and Sword & Shield Print {{TCG|Energy card|Basic Energy cards}}. All cards retained their original set number, but feature the Play! Pokémon logo as a [[Stamp_(TCG)|stamp]]. Each Booster pack contains 6 cards.

==Card list==
TPCi sublty published an official Card List on 24 October, 2023.<ref>[https://www.pokemon.com/static-assets/content-assets/cms2/pdf/trading-card-game/checklist/prize_pack_series_1_web_cardlist_en.pdf Pokémon TCG: Prize Pack—Series One Card List]</ref>

